org.eclipse.scada.configuration.modbus

Interface ModbusFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ModbusFactoryImpl

    public interface ModbusFactory
    The Factory for the model. It provides a create method for each non-abstract class of the model.
    See Also:
    ModbusPackage
